        <h2 class="group-title">
                            <a href="/web/20150105182558/http://www.bbc.co.uk/portuguese/topicos/curiosidades" class="group-title__link">Curiosidades</a>
                    </h2>
        <div class="hard-news-unit hard-news-unit--regular faux-block-link">



                <div class="hard-news-unit__image">
                        <div class="responsive-image responsive-image--16by9">
                                <div class="responsive-image__image js-delayed-image-load" data-src="/web/20150105182558oe_/http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/ws/200/amz/worldservice/live/assets/images/2015/01/02/150102025212_sp_vino_640x360_thinkstock_nocredit.jpg" data-width="640" data-height="360" data-alt="Credito: Thinkstock"></div>
                                <!--[if lt IE 9]>
                                    <img src="/web/20150105182558/http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/ws/200/amz/worldservice/live/assets/images/2015/01/02/150102025212_sp_vino_640x360_thinkstock_nocredit.jpg" class="responsive-image__image js-image-replace" alt="Credito: Thinkstock" width="640" height="360" />
                                <![endif]-->
                        </div>
                </div>
            <div class="hard-news-unit__body">
                <h3 class="hard-news-unit__headline">
                    <a href="/web/20150105182558/http://www.bbc.co.uk/portuguese/noticias/2015/01/150103_vinho_australia_lab" class="hard-news-unit__headline-link">
                        O país onde vinho está mais barato que água
                    </a>
                </h3>
                <p class="hard-news-unit__summary">Alta da moeda local, redução das exportações e excesso de produção derrubaram os preços dos vinhos na Austrália. </p>
